Package soot.dotnet.values

Class FunctionPointerConstant

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.Constant
      • soot.dotnet.values.FunctionPointerConstant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, EquivTo, Immediate, ConvertToBaf, Switchable, Value
    public class FunctionPointerConstant
extends Constant
    Function pointer constants point to a specific method. Note that these are temporary, as they get replaced with delegate handlers during the construction of .NET bodies.
    Author:
    Marc Miltenberger
